name: Tycho Celchu (V)
Lore: 'Spy fighting for the memory of his homeworld of Alderaan. Rogue Squadron pilot. Volunteered to fly an A-wing at the Battle of Endor. Former TIE fighter pilot.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to the power of anything he pilots. Tycho is a matching pilot for any starfighter. While piloting a starship, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise and it is immune to attrition < 4 (< 7 if stolen).',
